In [143]:
N_ves = len(points)

cells = []

for k in range(N_ves):
    
    (x, y) = (list(), list())
    pnt_id = vor.point_region[k]
    for idx in vor.regions[pnt_id]:
        x.append(vor.vertices[idx][0])
        y.append(vor.vertices[idx][1])
            
    vertices = np.array( [x, y] ).transpose()
    p = shp.Polygon(vertices)
    if abs(p.area()) - p.perimeter()*0.5 > 330.0: # lr = 0.5 margin
        cells.append( shp.Polygon(vertices) )
        p.draw()
print(len(cells),"compartments")
pol.draw()
plt.show()

cells[8].area()
cells[8].draw()

%%time
%%memit

d = tls.load_constants_from_file('/home/andrey/WORK/PyScripts/VesiclesInitialization/constants_for_fun_with_obstacles.txt')
d['lr'] = 0.5
#d['kl'] = 3.0
#d['kb'] = 0.5
for cell in cells_trials:
    
    print('PROGRESS : '+'#'*len(vesicles_out)+'_'*(len(cells_trials)-len(vesicles_out)))
    
    resize_value = (314.0 * 0.9/abs(cell.area()))**(1/2)
    shape = cell.make_nodes(113).resize(resize_value)
    V = shp.Variable(polygon=shape)
    
    AME = slv.ModEulerMethod(ADAPTIVE = True, parameters = [0.05, 0.9, 0.5, 2.0],
                             function = fnc.fun_with_obstacles,
                             t_step = 0.001, t_end = 500, frames = 4)
    #print(AME)
    
    out = AME.simulate(X = V,  walls = [cell], constants = d,
                       output = None, t_step_list = None, SILENT=False,
                       function = fnc.fun_with_obstacles)
    
    vesicles_out.append(out[-1])

In [157]:
xx = np.empty((len(vesicles_out),113))
yy = np.empty((len(vesicles_out),113))

for i in range(len(vesicles_out)):
    if fnc.geometry.area(vesicles_out[i].x(), vesicles_out[i].y())>0:
        xx[i] = vesicles_out[i].x()
        yy[i] = vesicles_out[i].y() 
    else:
        xx[i] = np.flipud(vesicles_out[i].x())
        yy[i] = np.flipud(vesicles_out[i].y())
